left this morng at 3 oclock to wards [-] ferey Whe cras over the Batle field of South Montin Near Bregettown this moring at 10 oclock A.M to the Pint of Recks Whe Pass thouth Binben at 12 None
and in Camp one mile below on the Calnoel and along Side of the Potmoc River 8 miles from Hopers farey Batle there as a going on for tow Days at Charlstown Whe march 16 miles to
Day The Rebls omestion tren to Night {2}

